text: :See Saint Sophia Church, Holy Wisdom#Churches for churches dedicated to Holy Wisdom (Sancta Sophia) Church buildings known as "Sofia Church": * Sofia Church, in Stockholm, named for Swedish queen Sophia of Nassau * Sofia Church, Jönköping, named for Sofia-Järstorp Parish, Jönköping, Sweden * Sofia Albertina Church, named for Sophia Albertina, Abbess of Quedlinburg (d. 1829) == See also == *List of churches dedicated to Holy Wisdom * Hagia Sophia (disambiguation) * Saint Sofia Church, Sofia (main historical church of Sofia, the capital of Bulgaria, the city being itself named after the church) * Ascension Cathedral (Sophia, Pushkin) * Sophienkirche, Dresden * Sophienkirche (Berlin), name for Sophia Louise of Mecklenburg-Schwerin
title: Sofia Church (disambiguation)
